\mu = \left(\frac{\nu_i}{\nu}\right)\frac{1}{\nu} + \left(1 - \frac{\nu_i}{\nu}\right)\left(\frac{\nu_i}{\nu}\right)\frac{2}{\nu} + \left(1 - \frac{\nu_i}{\nu}\right)^2\left(\frac{\nu_i}{\nu}\right)\frac{3}{\nu} + \ldots
 = \frac{\nu_i}{\nu^2} \left(1 + 2\left(1 - \frac{\nu_i}{\nu}\right) + 3\left(1 - \frac{\nu_i}{\nu}\right)^2 + \ldots\right)
 = \frac{\nu_i}{\nu^2} \left(\frac{1}{(1-\left(1 - \frac{\nu_i}{\nu}\right))^2}\right) = \frac{1}{\nu_i}
